description:
Slowly, but steadily, I'm working on my first collection. I want to thank all of you guys for the early support by everyone who joined my space in the first weeks on Soonaverse already and also everybody planning to still join our journey with this reward.

Please also drop your Twitter-Account-Adress - You never know, what other surprise might pop up. Or simply keep in touch.
name: Bombi Early Supporter Award
